{"name": "opentelemetry-container-distro", "metadata": {"name": "opentelemetry-container-distro", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/chrisguidry/opentelemetry-container-distro", "license": "", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["opentelemetry-api", "opentelemetry-exporter-otlp", "opentelemetry-instrumentation", "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-docker", "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-kubernetes", "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-process", "opentelemetry-sdk"], "summary": "An OpenTelemetry distro which automatically discovers container attributes", "upload_time": 1663501912}, "documentation": ["# opentelemetry-container-distro\n\nAn OpenTelemetry distro which automatically discovers container attributes.\n\nThis distro expands the standard `opentelemetry-distro` to automatically bring in\nadditional resource detectors for container environments.\n\n* [opentelemetry-resourcedetector-docker](https://pypi.org/project/opentelemetry-resourcedetector-docker/)\n* [opentelemetry-resourcedetector-kubernetes](https://pypi.org/project/opentelemetry-resourcedetector-kubernetes/)\n* [opentelemetry-resourcedetector-process](https://pypi.org/project/opentelemetry-resourcedetector-process/)\n\nOtherwise, this distro preserves the behavior and configuration of\n`opentelemetry-distro`.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerConfigurator", "bases": ["_OTelSDKConfigurator"], "methods": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerConfigurator.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "additional_detectors", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ResourceDetector", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.sdk.resources.ResourceDetector", "project": "opentelemetry-sdk"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerConfigurator._mocked_resource_create", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "auto_resource", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerConfigurator._configure", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Generally speaking, the beahvior of the opentelemetry-distro (just a thin layer over", "opentelemetry-sdk) is what I want to preserve here.  The only realy shortcoming of", "the opentelemetry-sdk implementation is that it doesn't allow you to inject", "resource detectors, and it is hardwired to use a very plain `Resource.create` call,", "which will use the OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES and/or OTEL_SERVICE_NAME to provide a", "very minimal Resource.", "The approach here will be to use mock to temporarily replace Resource.create with", "our own function. Although this couples tightly to the opentelemetry-sdk", "implementation, it is minimally invasive and doesn't require reproducing large swaths", "of opentelemetry.sdk._configuration.  Hopefully in a future version I can send an", "upstream PR to opentelemetry-sdk that allows for pluggable resource detectors through", "entrypoints as well."]}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerDistro", "bases": ["BaseDistro"], "methods": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OpenTelemetryContainerDistro._configure", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": [{"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro._OTelSDKConfigurator", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.sdk._configuration._OTelSDKConfigurator", "project": "opentelemetry-sdk"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.BaseDistro", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.instrumentation.distro.BaseDistro", "project": "opentelemetry-instrumentation"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.DockerResourceDetector", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry_resourcedetector_docker.DockerResourceDetector", "project": "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-docker"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.get_aggregated_resources", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.sdk.resources.get_aggregated_resources", "project": "opentelemetry-sdk"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.KubernetesDownwardAPIEnvironmentResourceDetector", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry_resourcedetector_kubernetes.KubernetesDownwardAPIEnvironmentResourceDetector", "project": "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-kubernetes"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.KubernetesDownwardAPIVolumeResourceDetector", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry_resourcedetector_kubernetes.KubernetesDownwardAPIVolumeResourceDetector", "project": "opentelemetry-resourcedetector-kubernetes"}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.mock", "xref": {"fqname": "unittest.mock", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry_container_distro.OTEL_TRACES_EXPORTER", "xref": {"fqname": "o